{
  "stem": "20405.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The new generation, what they know about it?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They don't know nothing about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But what animals, all of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Now, after that, we were talking about the revolution.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Before we get to that, let me just ask you, when the Hungarians were brought in to Birkenau, do you remember when this was, what time of year?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, at the end, before we got liberated, maybe about-- maybe in May was again.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Don't blame me, Carol, because I cannot remember everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It is impossible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I get so emotional when I say something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, I remember 50 years ago what happened to us, something impossible, something that human brains cannot imagine will happen.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No matter how the books writing or the pictures from the troops they're doing, is nothing like when you wearing their suffering every day.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's impossible for a human being-- I say that again-- to imagine what really we were suffering.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[CRYING] In the beginning, all the ashes from the oven, we were taking out, put 'em in a truck, and a couple Germans in the truck with three, four of us going to the nearest river was over there, the river called Vistula, and threw in the ashes over there.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But, of course, the ashes are very light.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all those ashes on the river was floating on top.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I don't know that river whether it was going to Poland or to Russian, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One day, they stop getting all those-- those ashes, because wasn't just ashes, it was bones, whole bones, because it don't becoming ashes.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "These whole bones, the bones, the big bones and so on, they don't become ashes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were still very hard.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
